{"tid":1483416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逃犯條例】黃之鋒：六四或在港重演　不主張港獨","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:08:03.000Z","uid":133680,"like":13,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"29635392ede035ddbdbc42552bc88996ce89ed5a","tid":1483416,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190818/s00001/1566103206928/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e9%bb%83%e4%b9%8b%e9%8b%92-%e5%85%ad%e5%9b%9b%e6%88%96%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e6%bc%94-%e4%b8%8d%e4%b8%bb%e5%bc%b5%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00001%2F1566103206928%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25bb%2583%25e4%25b9%258b%25e9%258b%2592-%25e5%2585%25ad%25e5%259b%259b%25e6%2588%2596%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%25bc%2594-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25bc%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrKg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=77df9dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00001%2F1566103206928%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25bb%2583%25e4%25b9%258b%25e9%258b%2592-%25e5%2585%25ad%25e5%259b%259b%25e6%2588%2596%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%25bc%2594-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25bc%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8&h=f63d5ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190818/s00001/1566103206928/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e9%bb%83%e4%b9%8b%e9%8b%92-%e5%85%ad%e5%9b%9b%e6%88%96%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e6%bc%94-%e4%b8%8d%e4%b8%bb%e5%bc%b5%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反《逃犯條例》修訂示威活動持續，有傳媒拍攝到有內地武警在深圳集結並進行演練。香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒接受美國之音訪問時表示，中央向香港派駐部隊並不能讓示威者噤聲，但港人應該意識到「六四天安門事件」也可能會在香港重演，故世界各地的領導人應該支持香港民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒日前在Twitter發帖文稱國家主席習近平應到香港與示威者會晤。在訪問中被問到是否習近平到港便能解決問題，黃之鋒表示，特首林鄭月娥只是代理人，習近平才是真正決策人。對於有媒體指反修例示威活動已影響香港經濟，並可能導致香港經濟陷入衰退，黃之鋒說，若《逃犯條例》修訂通過，才會真正侵蝕香港的政治和經濟自由。<br />\n<br />\n對於內地官方媒體指港人在發動「顏色革命」，香港示威帶有「顏色革命」色彩，黃之鋒重申，他不主張「香港獨立」，只是尋求香港有自由選舉。"},{"pid":"c7c7a1ac126c0f2e8afc7d60668bbf520fcb3785","tid":1483416,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24f99f19370050b4d141d768ac93bfc6d08c5c9","tid":1483416,"uid":13663,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhXPRxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhXPRxv.jpg&h=81c8b620&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ba348d65307d6f91dd8a6fd03f942681abb1110","tid":1483416,"uid":34334,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b74f8499a54f1d63e14270033c95be94773b47e3","tid":1483416,"uid":62815,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<br />\n佢又唔係大台<br />\n市民A講嘅嘢<br />\n同你同我講都係一樣份量啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891ca8110b9c504b557edd757715dc0fb139313e","tid":1483416,"uid":263349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"佢唔代表我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54de6f43325f2afaa48ae2e1de4ebcdc49b2be11","tid":1483416,"uid":156121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"佢講唔係都會變係<br />\n普選又好 自決又好<br />\n<br />\n結果都係港獨"},{"pid":"bcecd6a0ff5e5f5f01083707ba8776afe0a34696","tid":1483416,"uid":184379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,